South Africa’s Gold Industry Faces $100 Billion Silicosis Threat, RBC Says

-- B y   T o n y   B a r r e t t
-- 
2011-05-09T12:56:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/south-africa-s-gold-industry-faces-100-billion-silicosis-threat-rbc-says.html
South Africa ’s mining industry faces a
“very serious” threat from silicosis claims by workers, with
damage to gold producers possibly reaching $100 billion,  RBC
Capital Markets  said in a research report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
